Process called "test_from_basic" that takes suite_ptr as Integer returns Integer:
    @Reasoning
    Test basic FROM instruction: FROM ubuntu:20.04.
    @End Reasoning

    @Implementation
    Test round-trip of simple FROM instruction.
    @End Implementation

    Let dockerfile_source be "FROM ubuntu:20.04\n"
    proc test_round_trip from suite_ptr, "FROM basic", dockerfile_source

